# DevFest Annapolis 2025 - Claude Project Context

## Project Overview

This is the official website for DevFest Annapolis 2025, a free community-led software engineering conference organized by GDG Annapolis. The event takes place on November 15, 2025, at the AACC CALT Building in Arnold, Maryland.

**Live Site:** https://devfestannapolis-cavb908x9-jesse-altons-projects.vercel.app  
**GitHub:** https://github.com/mrmetaverse/devfestannapolis  
**Community:** https://matrix.to/#/#devfestannapolis:matrix.org

## Tech Stack & Architecture

### Core Technologies
- **Framework:** Next.js 15 (App Router with Turbopack)
- **Language:** TypeScript (strict mode)
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS v4
- **UI Library:** React 19.1.0
- **Icons:** Lucide React
- **Animation:** Framer Motion
- **Deployment:** Vercel

### Project Structure
```
devfestannapolis/
├── src/
│   ├── app/
│   │   ├── layout.tsx          # Root layout with SEO metadata
